00:19:20,950 --> 00:19:24,790
♫   It confuses me   ♫

239
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:28,450
♫   Because without even knowing   ♫

240
00:19:28,450 --> 00:19:31,090
♫   You’ve   ♫

241
00:19:31,090 --> 00:19:35,040
♫  grown so big  ♫

242
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:38,680
♫   All about you   ♫

243
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:42,250
♫  all about you my love  ♫

244
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:49,450
♫   I want to feel it without saying anything   ♫

245
00:19:49,450 --> 00:19:53,760
♫   I want to get a little closer to you   ♫

246
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:59,910
Now that he took out the Bead, did he become human

247
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:02,830
with the energy I gave him?

248
00:20:04,260 --> 00:20:07,580
I don't care either way.

249
00:20:10,770 --> 00:20:14,020
But why am I here again?

250
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:17,490
Old habits die hard.

251
00:20:17,490 --> 00:20:20,900
♫   Even if I wake up   ♫

252
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:22,760
♫  from this dream  ♫

253
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:28,420
♫   If you’re next to me   ♫

254
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:31,340
♫   I’m not afraid   ♫

255
00:20:31,340 --> 00:20:33,980
 She was crying.

256
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:42,010
♫   You are my all   ♫

257
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:49,560
You're always either oversleeping or hung over.

258
00:20:52,610 --> 00:20:55,330
Eat up. It's seonji hangover soup.

259
00:20:56,730 --> 00:21:00,560
Can you make bean sprout or dried pollack hangover soup next time?

260
00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:02,900
I don't want to see seonji anytime soon.

261
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:07,510
So hasty. I was just asking you to take note of it.

262
00:21:14,990 --> 00:21:17,070
 Do you feel better now?

263
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:19,970
 Let's go eat something good to help you feel better.

264
00:21:19,970 --> 00:21:21,870
 Let's meet up even if you don't want to.

265
00:21:21,870 --> 00:21:25,139
 I know it sounds a little weird, but just think of it as an assignment.

266
